OL,3,CMan jailed for 'horrific attack' that
OL,4,Cleft victim in a wheelchair
OL,6,FA man from South Gloucestershire has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed after stabbing a woman
OL,8,Fmultiple times and leaving her in a
OL,9,Fwheelchair.
OL,11,FOn the morning of Monday 11 September
OL,12,Flast year, police were called by
OL,13,Fambulance crews to the home of 56-year-
OL,14,Fold Ashley Joyner, in Shortwood Road,
OL,15,FPucklechurch.
OL,17,FHe had stabbed a 39-year-old woman six
OL,18,Ftimes and she was taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwith life-changing injuries.
