OL,3,CMan jailed for 'horrific attack' that
OL,4,Cleft victim in a wheelchair
OL,6,FThe attack has left the woman with
OL,7,Fpartial hearing loss and in need of a
OL,8,Fwheelchair.
OL,10,FJoyner was arrested by police and
OL,11,Fcharged the following day.
OL,13,FFollowing a four-day trial, the jury
OL,14,Ffound Joyner guilty of attempted
OL,15,Fmurder.
OL,17,FHe was sentenced to 27 years in prison
OL,18,Fat Bristol Crown Court on Tuesday 26
OL,19,FNovember.
