OL,4,Cleft victim in a wheelchair
OL,6,F"Due to the incident, it is unlikely I
OL,7,Fwill have full use of my right leg and
OL,8,Fnow have partial hearing in my right
OL,9,Fear. I will never be able to work
OL,10,Fagain and will have to use a
OL,11,Fwheelchair to get about.
OL,13,F"What kind of a selfish, manipulating
OL,14,Fperson he is. I cannot call him human
OL,15,For indeed an animal."
OL,17,FJoyner was also sentenced to eight
OL,18,Fmonths in prison, to run concurrently
OL,19,Fto the other sentence, for assault
OL,20,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
