OL,7,Fincident at a social club in
OL,8,FPucklechurch in July last year, where
OL,9,FJoyner had hit a man over the head
OL,10,Fwith a bottle in an unprovoked attack.
OL,12,FDC Mike Tarling said: "Joyner's
OL,13,Fhorrific and violent actions against
OL,14,Fthe victim have had a lasting impact
OL,15,Fand has forever changed her life.
